Contrarily, if \(e^{*}_{1}\) is an edge deletion such that \(G^{t}\subset G^{*}_{:1}\), we have:

\[\min_{G\in\mathcal{C}}\operatorname{GED}(\hat{G}^{t-1},G) >\min_{G\in\mathcal{C}}\operatorname{GED}(G^{*}_{:1},G), \tag{17}\]

